## ğŸ¯ Game Rules

1. Connect dots of the same color with continuous lines.
2. Lines cannot:
   - Cross other lines.
   - Pass through other dots.
   - Connect different colors.
3. All dots must be connected to complete a level.
4. Players must draw the line (tapping dots directly is not allowed).

